description:
Fastdev is a Swedish software development company founded in 2007 with the goal of delivering world-class software development services to its clients. Today we are a team of more than 100 specialists based in Stockholm or remote around the globe and we keep growing rapidly. The customers we work with are mainly Scandinavian companies operating in a variety of fields like financial, insurance, gaming, well-being, tourism, automotive, e-commerce and more. Our technological scope is just as diverse and covers front end/back end development, machine learning, IoT, cloud services and others.










 We are now looking for an Azure Integration Engineer to work on a project with one of our partners - a company that manages one of the biggest fast food franchises in the Nordic region, overseeing hundreds of restaurants across Denmark, Finland, Norway, and Sweden.










 You will be a great match if you have:









* A few years of experience in Azure integration development, specifically using C#, Logic Apps, MSSQL, Blob Storage, and Azure Functions;
* Proficient in C# with demonstrated ability to apply it in Azure-based environments;
* Proven experience with end-to-end integration development, from requirements gathering through deployment;
* Collaborative mindset, with strong communication skills for cross-departmental teamwork with product and business teams;
* Strong analytical and problem-solving skills, with the ability to navigate and resolve complex integration issues;
* Strong knowledge of Swedish and English.









 What is in there for you:









* A competitive remuneration, determined according to experience and achievements;
* A full-time regular employment opportunity;
* A hybrid work arrangement with a few days weekly in the Stockholm based office;
* The opportunity to collaborate with talented professionals in a supportive environment, fostering growth and skill development.
